snippet.title: Grimoire Groves - Official Gameplay Trailer | WLG Showcase 2024
snippet.description: See gameplay, explore a magical world, and learn more about Grimoire Groves in this latest trailer for the upcoming rogue-lite dungeon crawler game. In Grimoire Groves, you grow plants with magic, befriend magical creatures, and more. Grimoire Groves is coming to PC.
